722fe6d263c3d534077","tid":417264,"uid":14605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"智障爸爸，一年買一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178d7bba20c1f760d998c8859d0af81f9c3dcbdd","tid":417264,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T19:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>智障爸爸，一年買一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次來杭州，目的只有一個，就是要支持好友宋雲龍在杭州第一次舉辦的分享會。我認識他已經有半年了，親眼看見他的蛻變，今天他是一個充滿自信和魅力的導師，在台上發光發亮💡💡<br />\n雲龍兄，你一定可以把智富八道傳遍全中國的！👍🏻👍🏻💪💪⛽️⛽️<br />\n<br />\n同時，我也認識了杭州的朋友，他們也很熱情😊😊<br />\n希望有機會與你們相聚"},{"pid":"4756ba8ecf1918548e209b024a1e3b6e6c7c58c8","tid":417264,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恒大萬歲"},{"pid":"66e7ff55868aa6371a674ff9928f87e9e488de79","tid":417264,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恒大萬歲</blockquote><br />\n浸大萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}